{"tid":1422751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會就係將TG channel實體化","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T23:34:14.000Z","uid":135274,"like":186,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0032ad9eaa19c1a3828c25d6b1799301787b8681","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"1. 我地搞民間記者會就係希望打好輿論戰，所以<strong>我地做既只係不斷重複黑警既惡行，將精華部分不斷放大，係一個資訊發佈既平台</strong>，令黑警唔可以打溫情牌。<br />\n<br />\n2. 民間記者會一定要早於黑警既記者會，<strong>令到黑警每一日只可以回應我地既指控，搶佔輿論風向</strong>，甚至因為準備不足令到佢地醜態百出（例如：我手頭上冇資料）<br />\n<br />\n3. 為咗避免「大台化」，<strong>唔需要澄清立場，只需要不斷重複「五大訴求已經非常清晰」，以及解釋「光復香港，時代革命」係咩意思</strong>，以免進入隔空談判陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n4. 記者係唔會杯葛黑警記者會，因為咁係有違佢地既專業操守，<strong>所以我地要做既就係不斷提供彈藥，令黑警記者會失去佢既作用</strong>。"},{"pid":"0db654603acb69865cea27d95cb89eb13ca57f0f","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9f63e676efad7a9b787354f722502d398447db","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6d9fdaa8ba11d2781120a110a6edcd912c1f45","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921fb9bc4e55b9f0cb8eb4c43ef81159a9175469","tid":1422751,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"邊個做代表"},{"pid":"e98d63ff811bf6d8449d9d874f2a091af6630415","tid":1422751,"uid":199244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608c16f342727b1fe26a74274e5159d1dbd1377","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"921fb9bc4e55b9f0cb8eb4c43ef81159a9175469","tid":1422751,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"邊個做代表"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"如果可以既話，我希望係日日搵唔同人出席發言<br />\n<br />\n大家對代表性咁質疑係因為「記者會」本身俾人感覺係表達立場既平台，但如果我地將佢改為一個「資訊發佈」既模式，實際上係做緊一個媒體，你可以話你只係負責收集網民既材料。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔一定要stick with「記者會」呢個模式，實際上社區放映、連儂牆都係做緊呢啲嘢，只係「記者會」係coverage廣同埋最快速。"},{"pid":"64a3ecc3df3751f3e31e96c79fb8a91c841e50cc","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723ec5754b059c5d21d30c27d230caeb2bcd2123","tid":1422751,"uid":12149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"唔需要理代表性，只需要陳述事實，就唔需要理係代表邊個。事實係邊個代表都唔會有改變。state fact not opinion.<br />\n<br />\n重申訴求<br />\n強調警暴<br />\n譴責警黑"},{"pid":"79899483ba5689778293380b2f223b40725c0653","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"723ec5754b059c5d21d30c27d230caeb2bcd2123","tid":1422751,"uid":12149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"唔需要理代表性，只需要陳述事實，就唔需要理係代表邊個。事實係邊個代表都唔會有改變。state fact not opinion.<br />\n<br />\n重申訴求<br />\n強調警暴<br />\n譴責警黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"Exactly my point<br />\n<br />\n代表性問題係在於「表達立場」，但當我地立場好統一既時候，我只係出黎報導事實"},{"pid":"b78f0583819de2cfd3f5e5a63596335f2f6c80a1","tid":1422751,"uid":269256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"YES<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea82171f2a03a487715e572db90130787f2c2550","tid":1422751,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb6fcc59b769c051e7391b964fd655a9d1134e4","tid":1422751,"uid":135